title: Registered Voters by place of registration, New Hampshire, 2004
name: Registered Voters by place of registration, New Hampshire, 2004
description: The data for the map is derived from data uploaded by one of the contributors to Many Eyes". The table data was downloaded and geocoded. It shows the number of registered voters in New Hampshire by party affiliation in 2004.  NH has more independents voters than voters affiliated to either party.
